snippet.title: Path of Shadows (2013 Prototype) - The Graveyard
snippet.description:
The Graveyard - 1st Scenario of the prototype.

Path of Shadows, a stealth game made by 5 students.
The game is non-commercial and meant for learning/portfolio.

Web: http://thepathofshadows.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/pathofshadows

Song: Origamibiro - Flicker
